  "texts": [
    "Our survey differs from the survey conducted by Zhang et al. [26] in that our survey focuses on all deep neural networks employed for software engineering tasks.",
    "However, the survey conducted by Zhang et al.",
    "specifically concentrates on different representative LLMs.As a conclusion, although a few surveys have been made concerning the synergy between software engineering and deep learning, we still lack a clear picture of the advances, potentials, and challenges concerning deep learning-driven attempts at various software engineering tasks.",
    "To this end, in this paper, we select the most fundamental and most challenging software engineering tasks, and for each of them we analyze the advances, potentials, and challenges of its deep learning-based solutions.",
    "Requirements engineeringRequirements engineering (RE) is the process of eliciting stakeholder needs and desires and developing them into an agreed-upon set of detailed requirements that can serve as a basis for all subsequent development activities."
  ]
}